DATASET.TITLE: RNASeq_EGAS00001001306
DATASET.DESCRIPTION: RNASeq sequencing. Each library was sequenced using TruSeq SBS Kit v3-HS, in paired-end mode with a read length of 2 × 76 bp. We generated more than 20 million paired-end reads for each sample in a fraction of a sequencing lane on HiSeq2000 (Illumina Inc.) following the manufacturer’s protocol. Image analysis, base calling and quality scoring of the run were processed using the manufacturer’s software Real Time Analysis (RTA 1.13.48) and followed by generation of FASTQ sequence files.
